Introduction
============

$PKG_NAME is a project designed to... [Add specific details here].

This project uses the GNU Build System (Autotools).

Installation
============

See the file 'INSTALL' for general compilation instructions.

Briefly, the shell commands `./configure; make; make install` should
configure, build, and install this package.

The following configure options are specific to $PKG_NAME:

  --enable-debug  Enable debugging flags

Building from Git
=================

If you are building from the Git repository (rather than a release
tarball), you must first generate the build system infrastructure:

  ./bootstrap
  ./configure
  make

